quagga.input.subject: Re: Coral deals
quagga.input.body:
Why do we have so many deals from Coral that need to be assigned?



	Kevin Meredith@ENRON
	11/06/2000 10:58 AM
		 
		 To: Tana Jones/HOU/ECT@ECT
		 cc: Larry Joe Hunter/HOU/ECT@ECT
		 Subject: Coral deals

Tana,

Coral Energy Resources has six more deals from Thursday 11/02/00 that need to 
be assigned to Coral Energy Holdings.  The deal numbers are as follows:

Q74176.1
Q74562.1
Q74565.1
Q74569.1
Q75591.1
Q75597.1

These deals will have a status of "Pending - Sent to Legal" until I hear back 
from you.

Thank you.
Kevin
